<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Wed, 06 Apr 2022 06:22:31 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>Dyson Airwrap 升級版+新配件，發售日期 + 香港價錢</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/04/06/dyson-airwrap-3/shop_guide/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=dyson-airwrap-3</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 06 Apr 2022 06:22:31 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[買物情報]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1094469</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Dyson 今日公佈頭髮造型器 Dyson Airwrap 將推出升級版。升級版造型捲髮器可切換氣流方向，毋須 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Dyson 今日公佈頭髮造型器 Dyson Airwrap 將推出升級版。升級版造型捲髮器可切換氣流方向，毋須中途切換配件；產品也提供升級版順髮梳以及全新設計的康達抗毛躁風嘴配件。Dyson 指現有 Dyson Airwrap 用家可獨立購買新配件，直接為現有造型器升級。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Attachments-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094475" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Attachments-694x442.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="442" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Attachments-694x442.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Attachments-1280x816.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Attachments-768x489.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Attachments-1536x979.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Attachments-2048x1305.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Attachments-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-w_-Coanda-Smoothing-Dryer_2-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094476" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-w_-Coanda-Smoothing-Dryer_2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-w_-Coanda-Smoothing-Dryer_2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-w_-Coanda-Smoothing-Dryer_2-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-w_-Coanda-Smoothing-Dryer_2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-w_-Coanda-Smoothing-Dryer_2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-w_-Coanda-Smoothing-Dryer_2-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-w_-Coanda-Smoothing-Dryer_2-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Dyson Airwrap 造型器是一個利用到高速摩打產生康達氣流效應，毋須使用高溫度都可以塑造出用家理想的頭髮造型，大大減輕因高熱對頭髮造成的損傷。全新升級版 Dyson Airwrap 將加入升級版 30mm / 40mm Airwrap 髮捲，可配合用家造型而必換氣流方向，在造型過程中毋須更換配件，可更輕鬆一次過營造出外捲或內彎等波浪曲髮造型。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Stylist-Ritz-in-work_w_-Coanda-Smoothing-Dryer-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094480" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Stylist-Ritz-in-work_w_-Coanda-Smoothing-Dryer-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Stylist-Ritz-in-work_w_-Coanda-Smoothing-Dryer-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Stylist-Ritz-in-work_w_-Coanda-Smoothing-Dryer-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Stylist-Ritz-in-work_w_-Coanda-Smoothing-Dryer-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Stylist-Ritz-in-work_w_-Coanda-Smoothing-Dryer-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Stylist-Ritz-in-work_w_-Coanda-Smoothing-Dryer-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Stylist-Ritz-in-work_w_-Coanda-Smoothing-Dryer-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-B_after-1-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094477" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-B_after-1-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-B_after-1-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-B_after-1-600x900.jpg 600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-B_after-1-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-B_after-1-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-B_after-1-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-B_after-1-scaled.jpg 1067w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></a></p><p>升級版 Dyson Airwrap 也加入了以下兩個新配件：全新設計的康達抗毛躁風嘴，可把 Dyson Airwrap 變成風力強勁的風筒，吹乾頭髮並隱藏毛躁髮絲，也避免頭髮過熱。</p><p>產品也會加入升級版順髮梳，用家可更容易塑造到更順直、更整齊的直髮效果。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-A_After-3-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094479" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-A_After-3-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-A_After-3-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-A_After-3-600x900.jpg 600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-A_After-3-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-A_After-3-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-A_After-3-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Model-A_After-3-scaled.jpg 1067w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></a></p><p>Dyson Airwrap Complete 多功能造型器即日發售，建議零售價為 HK$4,480，備有鎳銀色、桃紅色，以及 Dyson.hk 及 Dyson 體驗店獨家型號銅色與普魯士藍色。現有 Dyson Airwrap 用家，亦可獨立購買上述最新配件，可供獨立選購的配件將於 5 月發售。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Colourways-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1094474" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Colourways-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Colourways-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Colourways-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Colourways-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Colourways-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Colourways-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Colourways-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>資料來源：Dyson</p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=JdgKrv8Ma1Q:cKOjZcM_7kw:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=JdgKrv8Ma1Q:cKOjZcM_7kw:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Apple WWDC 2022 公佈舉行日期，料推出 iOS 16, 新版 macOS</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/04/06/apple-wwdc-2022/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=apple-wwdc-2022</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 06 Apr 2022 05:00:33 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[手提電話]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category><category><![CDATA[WWDC 2022]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1094462</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Apple 每年都會舉辦 WWDC 開發者大會，藉以公佈關於 Apple 軟件包括 iOS, iPadOS 等 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Apple 每年都會舉辦 WWDC 開發者大會，藉以公佈關於 Apple 軟件包括 iOS, iPadOS 等等的改革。Apple WWDC 2022 今年就會在 6 月 6 日至到 6 月 10 日，同樣會在網上舉行，部份人士會被邀請到 Apple Park 觀看 keynote 影片。</p><p>每年 WWDC 都會有最新軟件消息，而今年好大機會發表 iOS 16, iPadOS 16, watchOS 9, tvOS 16，還有最新版本的 macOS。開發者大會將會從 6 月 6 日在網上舉行，屆時將會舉辦多個網上開發者專題講座。不過 6 月 6 日的 keynote 發佈會將會邀請一批少數的開發者、學生到 Apple Park 現場參與觀看影片，名額有限，詳情可參閱 Apple Developer 網站。</p><p>Apple 更宣佈將再次舉辦 Swift Student Challenge，這個活動歡迎全球各地學生參與，透過 Swift Playgrounds 這個 iPad/Mac 應用程式編寫 Swift 語言，在 4 月 25 日之前提交一個任由學生自訂主題的項目作品。詳情可瀏覽 Swift Student Challenge 網站。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/hk/newsroom/2022/04/apples-worldwide-developers-conference-returns-in-its-all-online-format/">Apple</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=8KtMZMFthpg:FmBuhx-gYpU:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=8KtMZMFthpg:FmBuhx-gYpU:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【評測】DJI Mic 無線收音咪，充電盒設計 + 配件多 + 續航力高</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/04/06/dji-mic/dc/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=dji-mic</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Harold]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 06 Apr 2022 00:55:58 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[數碼相機]]></category><category><![CDATA[相機配件]]></category><category><![CDATA[評測]]></category><category><![CDATA[DJI Mic]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1086877</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>近年拍攝用無線咪推陳出新，有 RODE 的 Wireless GO2，棄用傳統有駁收音線的錄音方式，把線和收音 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>近年拍攝用無線咪推陳出新，有 RODE 的 Wireless GO2，棄用傳統有駁收音線的錄音方式，把線和收音咪融為一體，DJI 推出的 DJI Mic 亦跟隨這潮流。DJI Mic 無線收音咪大有驚喜，只看外觀也可感受到其革新之處，加上加入了不少方便的配件，絕對便利拍攝。廢話少講，讓小編馬上開箱測試。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086998 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07133-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07133-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07133-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07133-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07133-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07133.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲DJI Mic</p><h2>配件充足，收納袋容量大</h2><p>開盒後，裡面有個以斜紋外觀的收納袋，上面印有 DJI 標誌。收納袋內有一條 USB-C 的充電線、 1 條 2 頭 3.5MM 的駁線，以連接接收器和相機。亦有 2 隻俗稱「Dead Cat」的防風套。小編認為收納袋尺寸適中，可把所有錄音需用的配件都放妥。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086968 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07140-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07140-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07140-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07140-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07140-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07140.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲斜紋外觀的收納袋，可放置所需配件</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086969 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07144-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07144-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07144-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07144-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07144-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07144.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ USB-C 的充電線</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086970 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07143-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07143-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07143-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07143-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07143-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07143.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 1 條 2 頭 3.5MM 的駁線</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086971 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07142-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07142-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07142-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07142-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07142-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07142.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 2 個防風套</p><h2>顏色型格，設計似耳機盒</h2><p>充電盒顏色和設計可謂一絕， 而且扎實。正面看來，有凹凸坑紋設計，而頂部使用霧面磨砂材質，並刻有 DJI 標誌，感覺頗高級。機身後面就簡單地設有一個 USB-C 充電口。類似真無線耳機盒，都是以充電盒二次供電。在機盒正面，可見 4 顆燈，用來顯示剩餘電量。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086972 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07098-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07098-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07098-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07098-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07098-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07098.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲設計似耳機盒，有凹凸坑紋</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086973 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07101-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07101-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07101-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07101-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07101-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07101.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲頂部使用霧面磨砂材質，刻有 DJI 標誌，感覺頗高級</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086974 aligncenter" src="https:/