639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲盒內基本配件</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086977 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07118-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07118-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07118-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07118-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07118-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07118.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ USB-C 和 Lightning 插頭</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086978 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07116-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07116-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07116-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07116-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07116-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07116.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086980 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07122-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07122-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07122-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07122-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07122-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07122.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-