h: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086984 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07120-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07120-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07120-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07120-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07120-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07120.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Lightning 可插入到 iPhone 收音</p><h2>細少輕巧，磁吸收音咪</h2><p>收音咪上手感覺細少較輕，只有 30 克，依舊印有 DJI 標誌和斜紋。正上方是收音位置，以及 1 個外置咪插口。旁邊是數據傳輸 USB-C 插口和開關掣。另一邊則是錄音掣和連結按鈕。後面當然是一個夾，方便用家在收音時夾在衣領上。另外加附了 1 粒磁力頗大的磁石，有時未能夾在衣領上，可轉作磁吸。受惠於輕巧機身，夾在衫上未有變形。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1087002 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07108-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07108-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07108-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07108-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07108-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07108.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲收音咪後的夾和磁石</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086987 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07152-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07152-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07152-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07152-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07152-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07152.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲方便用家在收音時夾在衣領上</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086988 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07154-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07154-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07154-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07154-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07154-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07154.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086989 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07157-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07157-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07157-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07157-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07157-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07157.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有時未能夾在衣領上，可轉作磁吸</p><p>接收器同是斜紋質感，上方是個顯示器，下方是一個插槽和充電位置。側面是 1 個接駁相機插頭和 1 個耳機插頭作監聽之用。另一邊是開關掣和 USB-C 插口。今次顯示器大有驚喜，是觸控螢幕，可以操控所有功能，未有如其他收音咪般直接，假如要控制收音音量大小，要按多個按鈕，方可成功調節，需要一定時間熟習。此外，可裝冷熱靴轉接於接收器上，供相機接駁之用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086990 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07112-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07112-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07112-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07112-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07112-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07112.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086991 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07111-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07111-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07111-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07111-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07111-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07111.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲冷熱靴轉接於接收器上</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086993 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07135-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07135-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07135-1-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07135-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07135-1-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07135-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086994 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07137-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07137-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07137-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07137-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07137-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07137.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可將接收器插在冷熱靴上</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086995 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07138-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07138-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07138-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07138-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07138-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07138.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳機插頭作監聽之用</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1087000 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07131-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07131-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07131-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07131-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07131-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07131.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲假如要控制收音音量大小，要按多個按鈕，方可成功調節</p><h2>連接快且遠，聲音響亮</h2><p>DJI Mic 的連接速度可謂迅雷不及掩耳，基本上只要拿出接收器，即可收音。小編認為音質清晰無雜音，拍攝 Vlog、訪問、或戲劇都絕對可以，完全對得起這個價位。收音範圍廣，官方指最遠可連接到 250 米外，小編在公司範圍行走，未見有斷線情況。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086996 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07110-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07110-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07110-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07110-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07110-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07110.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲只要拿出接收器，即可收音</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086997 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07159-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07159-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07159-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07159-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07159-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07159.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小編在公司範圍行走，未見有斷線情況</p><h2>續航力不俗</h2><p>接收器的續航力有 5.5 小時，收音咪則各有 5 小時。加上配合充電盒，共有 15 小時可使用，電量絕對足夠應付拍攝。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086999 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07100-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07100-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07100-2-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07100-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07100-2-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/DSC07100-2.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲續航力共有 15 小時</p><h2>總結：實用性高，惟操控未夠直接</h2><p>DJI Mic 的突破可見一班，利用充電盒為收音咪充電，亦可當作收納之用，絕對超越同類產品。其實用性高，可透過不同插頭，轉換不同裝置。唯一要挑剔之處是操控性，觸控螢幕固然創新，但不易轉換指令。但整體來說，適合所有需要拍攝之人。</p></p><div class="feedflare">
